.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD3fg4Ut1SB_itHxHWWPNUNykhOULs9kJY3V_8tGHckhw&oe=66E81FA7"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "2738807569571714", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12386448_315258945476102_1813863411_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=L44mqyniUl4Q7kNvgFJiPzR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDxZetiZIsWxxLTP1FwZb_yTNZI1kC1bp7j-FHkpcaOIQ&oe=66E7FD93"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "258485008493558", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12522403_605953636231970_1698927185_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VyiGLaqm3RQQ7kNvgFqtZ8O&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCE-NHunwSR4n7sh5Wj70i21Uk4DMC8v0h8213q9XMnKg&oe=66E830D5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Specular Theory", "keywords": ["Virtual Reality", "360 video", "Movies", "Cinematic", "Behind the scenes"], "long_description": "The world is not flat, our view of it shouldn\u2019t be either. Download our app to get your ongoing dose of the best VR experiences, created by Specular Theory and our featured partners.  This is a one\u00adstop place to\nfind premium experiences and award\u00adwinning VR content including music and entertainment, ST\noriginals and other fun experiments we\u2019ve shot along the way!\n\nWelcome to anti\u00adflat entertainment.\n\nSpecular Theory was founded in 2013 to break new ground in the realm of immersive media content.\nConstantly at the forefront of this rapidly changing field, the studio\u2019s developers customize immersive\ntechnologies to uniquely amplify the storytelling for each individual project. Collaborating with clients\nfrom Fortune 500 companies to major film studios to indie filmmakers, Specular Theory has built an\nunparalleled track record for crafting startlingly effective new narratives using immersive technologies.\n\nHave feedback? Need help? Email us at: hello@speculartheory.com.\n", "short_description": "Download our app to g